    <noscript>
      <div style="font-family:sans-serif;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;padding:24px">
        <h1>Click the Red Button - Discover Random Cool Websites</h1>
        <p>Your gateway to the internet's coolest, weirdest, and most addictive random websites. Discover 360+ curated games, art, and fun sites with one click. Start exploring now!</p>

        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p>Simply click the big red button and get instantly transported to a random website from our hand-picked collection. No algorithms, no tracking — just pure internet discovery.</p>

        <h2>Browse by Category</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>All</strong> — A surprise mix of art, fun, and games from across the web</li>
          <li><strong>Games</strong> — Browser-based games, classic arcade titles, and fun puzzles</li>
          <li><strong>Art</strong> — Creative tools, generative art, visual experiments, and digital galleries</li>
          <li><strong>Fun</strong> — Weird, wonderful, and wildly entertaining corners of the internet</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Why Click the Red Button?</h2>
        <p>We've curated over 360 unique websites so you can rediscover how awesome the internet can be. Whether you're looking for fun sites to visit, cool random websites, weird internet stuff, or amazing websites you didn't know existed — you're in the right place.</p>
        <p>Our shuffle system ensures you never see the same site twice within a session, and sites are pre-loaded for instant discovery with zero loading lag.</p>

        <h2>Features</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>360+ hand-picked websites across three categories</li>
          <li>No duplicate sites within a browsing session</li>
          <li>Save favorites to revisit anytime</li>
          <li>Track your browsing history</li>
          <li>Earn achievements as you explore</li>
          <li>Works on desktop and mobile</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Explore the Internet</h2>
        <p>From iconic classics to bizarre little web toys, every click is a new adventure. Dive into interactive art, classic games, creative experiments, and the internet's most unforgettable discoveries — all in one place.</p>

